data.text:
Wombling Free - The Movie DVD

|

Based on the popular BBC series 'Wombling Free' follows the adventures of the furry loveable litter-pickers from Wimbledon Common - The Wombles. Only seen by those who believe in them their work goes largely unnoticed until a young girl Kim spots them. When she invites them to her birthday party her mother is forced to believe when she comes face to face with Orinoco Tobermory and the rest of the gang. A public meeting is set up to prove once and for all that the Wombles to exist and should be helped with their quest to clean up the common. But on the day in question... a bad storm breaks out over the common. Will the inhabitants of Wimbledon actually be able to see their cuddly crusaders? [show more]
